*"Zaboravi* da se sutra sastajemo na parku" (Forget that we are meeting at the park tomorrow). 

*"Zaboravila* je njenu torbu kada je otišla" (She forgot her bag when she left). 

*"Zaboravio* je svoje ključeve" (He forgot his keys). 

*"Ona će se zaboraviti* vremenom" (She will be forgotten with time). 

*"Mogu li da *zaboravim* da se dogodilo?" (Can I forget that it happened?). 

*"On je *zaboravio* da plati račun" (He forgot to pay the bill).